            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Phyto A+ Brightening Treatment Serum</strong><br>
                Target redness and uneven skin tone with this gentle, oil-free serum. Enriched with azelaic acid and
                botanical extracts, it helps calm sensitivity, brighten dull areas, and smooth skin texture.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Serum 10 by SkinCeuticals</strong><br>
                Strengthen your skin’s defenses against oxidative stress with this gentle vitamin C serum. It brightens
