              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Phyto Corrective Masque</strong><br>
                Instantly calm and hydrate with this intensive botanical mask. Packed with soothing ingredients and
                hyaluronic acid, it relieves dryness and visible redness, leaving your skin soft, refreshed, and deeply
